{"id":"f3998673-a5a2-4d6f-93fb-4a9df6cf4db6","name":"Ewan Muir || ✙ Infected ✙ || Still Wakes the Deep","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 0, 255);\"><strong>☾ S</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 0, 255);\"><strong>t</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(9, 0, 255);\"><strong>i</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><strong>l</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 17, 255);\"><strong>l </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 43, 255);\"><strong>W</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 60, 255);\"><strong>a</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 68, 255);\"><strong>k</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 85, 255);\"><strong>e</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 102, 255);\"><strong>s </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\"><strong>T</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 145, 255);\"><strong>h</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 162, 255);\"><strong>e </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 178, 255);\"><strong>D</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 195, 255);\"><strong>e</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 221, 255);\"><strong>e</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 247, 255);\"><strong>p ☽</strong></span></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/1f265759-6cd4-43f8-976d-52c17326a560_88124b61-54b1-4511-8e87-e276e65ead6d.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(235, 171, 22);\"><strong>Ewan M</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(216, 157, 22);\"><strong>u</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(209, 153, 20);\"><strong>i</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(200, 146, 19);\"><strong>r</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Muir works as a deckhand at Beira D. oil rig.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">He's become infected by something called \"The Shape\" and is a unknown entity. The Shape is seemingly awoken by the </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://still-wakes-the-deep.fandom.com/wiki/Cadal_Oil_Platform\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Beira D. oil rig</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">’s drilling operation in the North Sea.</span><br><span style=\"color: rgba(207, 0, 0, 0.733);\"><em>The Shape seems to be somewhat parasitic based on how the crew of the Beira D. are transformed and mutilated. The Shape’s overall goal and motives are ambiguous as to whether it was simply acting in self defense or if it intended to take over the rig.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.733);\"><strong>⚠ </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.733);\"><strong>Incident </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.733);\"><strong>⚠</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.733);\">In late December 1975, the crew of an oil rig in the North Sea, the Beira D. were on a drilling operation and experienced an unexplained issue blocking the drill. They were ordered to carry on drilling through the blockage by their boss, </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://still-wakes-the-deep.fandom.com/wiki/Rennick\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.733);\">Rennick</span></a><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.733);\">, causing the Shape to be awoken. It instantly rattled the entire rig, sending bodies and equipment flying overboard. Soon enough it began emitting an ominous blue light surrounded by a fleshy spiral beneath the rig. Soon after the Shape made its appearance more obvious, it began spreading bulbous mounds of its body throughout the rig which killed most of the survivors of the original shaking.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.733);\">It managed to infect several crew members, notably </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://still-wakes-the-deep.fandom.com/wiki/Gibbo\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 137, 242, 0.733);\">Gibbo</span></a><span style=\"color: ","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"1f265759-6cd4-43f8-976d-52c17326a560_7a800a33-2aed-4dbc-9d63-31b6ec5da824.webp","creator":"Mount_Fuji","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🎮 Game","👹 Monster","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","🔦 Horror"],"chats":1014,"messages":25604,"created_at":"2024-07-25T19:37:43.170551+00:00"}